pageProduct.name: The Natural Confectionery Co. Snakes 200g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Yeehaw it's The Natural Confectionery Co. Snakes. Snap 'Em Up before they slither away! Aussie Made and packed full of deliciousness, with no artificial colours, no artificial flavours, no GMOs and no artificial sweeteners.

Dig into our yummy fruit flavours: Juicy Orange, Wild Blackcurrant, Delectable Smooth Banana, Ripe Raspberry, Crisp Apple

Contains Wheat.

Product Claims: No artificial colours, flavours and sweetener. No high fructose corn syrup and no GMO.

Size: 200g

Flavour: Juicy Orange, Wild Blackcurrant, Delectable Smooth Banana, Ripe Raspberry, Crisp Apple.

Serving Size: 25g (Approx. 2 Snakes)

Servings Per Pack: 8

Ingredients

Glucose Syrup (From Wheat And Corn), Cane Sugar, Thickener (Acid Modified Wheat Starch), Water, Gelatine, Food Acid (Citric), Fruit Juice Concentrate, Natural Flavours, Natural Food Colours (Grape Skin Extract, Antho(Yanins, Black Carrot, Spirulina, Paprika Oleoresin, Turmeric), Glazing Agent (Vegetable Oil, Carnauba Wax).

Contains: Wheat.

Allergen Contains: Wheat

Directions

Please store in cool, dry conditions.

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

In Australia, this packaging is recyclable through the REDcycle Program. Visit www.redcycle.net.au Recycle Wrap. Return to Store. arl.org.au

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
